      "text": [
        " غُرْفَةِ أُمِّ إِبْرَاهِيمَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1119 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"The Prophet (sw) once fell from a horse, injuring the right side of his body, and he led the people in prayer while seated in the room of Umm Ibrahim”."
        ]
      }
